<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8" standalone="no"?><?Xpress productLine="ncc-clause" ?><clause id="_0fb27a91-2baa-476d-9575-bb54ec513b39" outputclass="ncc-clause" variation="VIC"><sptc>E3P4</sptc><title id="_b433cec2-c03f-4705-8a68-b9353f8875bc">Design, construction and installation</title><archive-num>2019: FP1.4</archive-num><subclause id="_65fc618c-bab9-400b-96fb-3f46dc295ffc" outputclass="subclause"><title id="_a80a7a72-9066-4be5-badc-468230d8251c">SubClause</title><num>1</num><p>A roof drainage system must ensure the following—</p><ol outputclass="alpha"><li id="_ae0e0542-9685-4daf-b740-14ddb9e2299e">Stormwater is transferred to a <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/1c3f2f74-4ee1-4cdd-b1b4-53c91069d002/1403_3.16.0.xml#_7df493b5-1832-40a0-b9d0-d2fb3fec5d98" id="_29e78913-174f-4bfc-afbc-917b53f22654" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">point of connection</xref>.</li><li id="_c742688d-8031-498b-9f21-e4b8beb9e483">Access for maintenance and clearing <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/1c3f2f74-4ee1-4cdd-b1b4-53c91069d002/1209_1.2.0.xml#_417d94d8-f254-4788-9a14-c4c5da89daa6" id="_ea178c9e-a238-4d3f-92e9-a7f1da4bdb07" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">blockages</xref>.</li></ol></subclause><subclause id="_b76c77ee-9e22-46aa-a8da-d5a28126480b" outputclass="subclause"><title id="_bfc257ad-4b6d-4642-8659-c0f1706c3dd6">SubClause</title><num>2</num><p>A roof drainage installation must avoid the following—</p><ol outputclass="alpha"><li id="_06ddd24e-9a54-47f8-991f-f299ea7ee434"><xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/1c3f2f74-4ee1-4cdd-b1b4-53c91069d002/1362_2.0.0.xml#_ba5bd5ee-ef5f-41be-b153-43835028cd86" id="_d16bcf17-722e-404c-8bf5-f230d701d674" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">Loss</xref> of <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/1c3f2f74-4ee1-4cdd-b1b4-53c91069d002/1186_0.6.0.xml#_905252bf-2ff1-43f8-ae81-2949aa116fee" id="_c64efbca-ff48-4599-a86d-10aa39794a72" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">amenity</xref> due to <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/1c3f2f74-4ee1-4cdd-b1b4-53c91069d002/1209_1.2.0.xml#_417d94d8-f254-4788-9a14-c4c5da89daa6" id="_3158ca71-6832-441c-b1f0-41b497d6b0e7" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">blockages</xref> and <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/1c3f2f74-4ee1-4cdd-b1b4-53c91069d002/1500_27.0.0.xml#_0ece1af9-d663-4f17-a7c9-bf59ebb1b1ef" id="_7b57db3b-76aa-45ec-99ac-6fd9d8eb9a47" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">uncontrolled discharge</xref>.</li><li id="_fb9e47fc-c2a7-498f-a00b-3736a91134d3">Foul air and gases accumulating in the roof drainage system.</li><li id="_2588756d-5a2a-42d7-9ba3-a5f5ddfd27e7"><xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/1c3f2f74-4ee1-4cdd-b1b4-53c91069d002/1362_2.0.0.xml#_ba5bd5ee-ef5f-41be-b153-43835028cd86" id="_7ecd336e-7b91-4067-95a4-86364c140ce7" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">Loss</xref> to buildings and property <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/1c3f2f74-4ee1-4cdd-b1b4-53c91069d002/1186_0.6.0.xml#_905252bf-2ff1-43f8-ae81-2949aa116fee" id="_c3cc76ab-2c6a-4737-8180-99de488feadd" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">amenity</xref> due to <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/1c3f2f74-4ee1-4cdd-b1b4-53c91069d002/1209_1.2.0.xml#_417d94d8-f254-4788-9a14-c4c5da89daa6" id="_b89a271e-cf06-414c-954f-c133d3702a3d" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">blockages</xref> and <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/1c3f2f74-4ee1-4cdd-b1b4-53c91069d002/1500_27.0.0.xml#_0ece1af9-d663-4f17-a7c9-bf59ebb1b1ef" id="_08fdd782-ffb0-4d7b-923e